lead_paragraph: Bayern Munich attacking midfielder Mario Goetze returned to training on Monday for the first time since October but defender Javi Martinez could be ruled out for weeks with a knee injury.

headline.print_headline: Goetze Back in Bayern Training, Martinez Faces Layoff
